contents:
Per Curiam,
Learned counsel for appellees very fairly suggest that this proceeding is apparently an effort to resubmit a matter which has already been considered and passed upon: Peoples Trust Company of Pittsburgh v. Safe Deposit and Trust Company of Pittsburgh, 259 Pa. 62; but, be this’ as it may, the appeal is dismissed on the opinion of the learned court below sustaining the demurrers to the bili and dismissing it.
